Name: Official Wicked Vixen Whack-A-Dick Pro
About the game: Imagine Whack-A-Mole... but with dicks. In this mini-game, you will find yourself trapped in a hole-filled box surrounded by more than 40 big red dicks. Press START and whack them off until time runs out! Then pass the headset to the next person at your party and see who can get the highest score! Remember, you can't just grab them... you've got to whack them! *This game was designed with Oculus Quest and Rift in mind. Additional access through OpenVR is in development. Wicked Vixen has many more ideas for additional gameplay. This is an Early Access game that will have updates and additions over time. Have your own ideas? Send us an email! @@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@ Support for SteamVR has just been added... contact us if you have any issues running on anything other than Oculus platforms. If you have trouble, verify the install path. When you pull up Whack A Dick in your library you should see a gear icon to the right. In there, you should see a 'Manage' option and then a 'Browse Local Files' option. That should open your file explorer and you should see a folder that says 'SteamVROnly.' If you open that folder, you should see a 'WhackADickProSteamVR.exe' file. @@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@@
